personalizing your experience, and just helping you make the most of our service. We also process your data to keep you and all of our members safe and secure while using our service. We take this responsibility very seriously and we’re always working to improve our systems and processes to help protect you. And yes, we process your data to show relevant ads –
you can control this in your settings. Read on for a more detailed explanation.
For information on how we process personal data through “profiling” and “automated decision-making”, please see our
FAQ
