CCPA Privacy Statement
For California Consumers
This California section supplements the
Privacy Policy
and applies solely to California consumers (excluding our personnel). The Table below describes how we process California consumers’ personal information (excluding our personnel), based on definitions laid out in the California Consumer Privacy Act, as amended by the California Privacy Rights Act ("CCPA").
Not all of the items listed in the Table below are relevant to you.
For example, we do not collect Social Security numbers from our users
, but we may collect this data in the course of evaluating a job applicant.
